{"tid":2383802,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泫雅這麼瘦竟然還有「戀愛肥」！為了讓沒食慾DAWN多吃點，自己胖了5kg","createTime":"2021-01-28T06:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T07:27:45.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dd1a45190320459fcc499e63867e65a5601c5a0a","tid":2383802,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:46:00.000Z","msg":"有著性感小野馬之稱的南韓愛豆泫雅自從認愛同為歌手的DAWN後就完全是一副癡情小女友的模樣，三句話不離男友。<br />\n<br />\n泫雅和DAWN戀愛6年，按理說早就過了熱戀期，但兩人卻依舊如膠似漆，經常在IG上曬幸福照，男友還陪泫雅健身、逛街、看展覽，甚至穿同款衣服，一句話就是甜到齁人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9d95b72bc434bcd9bf848592849bcfdf/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133296-894936.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9d95b72bc434bcd9bf848592849bcfdf%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133296-894936.jpg&h=a47e31cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d726b0b8aab85556e587b8c3121cc7a0/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133296-894937.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d726b0b8aab85556e587b8c3121cc7a0%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133296-894937.png&h=cd71bddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近泫雅受邀參加了時尚雜誌《W Korea》YouTube採訪，提起男友，滿臉的幸福笑容，更自曝戀愛太舒心，自己不小心就胖了。 泫雅透露自己最愛DAWN工作時的樣子，因為認真工作的男人最帥氣。 「我倆雖然是戀人，但也是企鵝頭，每次看到他工作的狀態或是聽到那些還沒有被公開的歌曲，對我來說都是一種鞭策，敦促自己要好好上課，要多多練習。 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_aba9045c3b6f4ab0fa1c44ea15dbbd6b/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133296-894938.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_aba9045c3b6f4ab0fa1c44ea15dbbd6b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133296-894938.png&h=fb774610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都說逃不過「戀愛肥」，擁有魔鬼身材的泫雅也是這樣，「談戀愛期間胖了5kg。 其實我自己也屬於那種 為了讓不喜歡吃的人，但DAWN屬於吃一頓感覺能撐好幾天，他幾乎沒有食慾，我經常拉著他吃吃喝喝（為了讓他多吃），就這樣很公平地都長了肉了，雖然現在又瘦了，但確實之前胖過。 」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8bc5dd27c5e52cf569a3bd4fad883385/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-27/133296-894939.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8bc5dd27c5e52cf569a3bd4fad883385%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-27%2F133296-894939.png&h=9b087fae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泫雅說，DAWN的存在就是她的幸福。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5sQxRp_zmBw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5sQxRp_zmBw&d=LvSu6Mc%2FVB7R449T953cU%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=3d71f810\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5sQxRp_zmBw</a>"},{"pid":"7d1fdc43c3d035c6e1e597979342aaba3843513a","tid":2383802,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:51:15.000Z","msg":"韓國崩壞之最 係泫雅定娜恩？"},{"pid":"45d5b39c3a3bb0931f8af1b78cb04364e1cf0b91","tid":2383802,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:54:15.000Z","msg":"彩都有，成日俾紋身師中出食避孕丸食到肥晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0dc3736cf2555d1150475a5e9d36cb7b968a1b","tid":2383802,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T06:56:03.000Z","msg":"癲雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29cadd999c568f368df67923bcdde6bdb5b16db","tid":2383802,"uid":77461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T07:03:37.000Z","msg":"第二張密集恐懼症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3b332254e52d0a6f3524fb6c8893a54a1322ea","tid":2383802,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45d5b39c3a3bb0931f8af1b78cb04364e1cf0b91","tid":2383802,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sco